<subSubSection id="C350656FAE37FFAEFF753FCDFCCCD581" pageId="1" pageNumber="554" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph id="8BF536E4AE37FFAEFF753FCDFCCCD581" blockId="1.[151,1436,1198,1369]" pageId="1" pageNumber="554">
<emphasis id="B93EEAF6AE37FFAEFF753FCDFEF8D5A4" bold="true" box="[151,274,1198,1224]" pageId="1" pageNumber="554">Diagnosis.</emphasis>
Antenna black; stylus thick, finger-like, similar to first flagellomere. Palpus black. Pterostigma rather narrow, posterior margin far from R 
<subScript id="17CE34A1AE37FFAEFDCB3F86FDA8D59F" attach="left" box="[553,578,1253,1267]" fontSize="6" pageId="1" pageNumber="554">2+3</subScript>
. Halter dark brown.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
