<collectingCountry id="F35D7674AE37FFAEFE853F94FE40D47D" box="[359,426,1271,1297]" name="China" pageId="1" pageNumber="554">China</collectingCountry>
(
<collectingRegion id="498EF806AE37FFAEFE5B3F94FDE2D47D" box="[441,520,1271,1297]" country="China" name="Henan" pageId="1" pageNumber="554">Henan</collectingRegion>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="C350656FAE37FFAEFF253E78FD65D435" pageId="1" pageNumber="554" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8BF536E4AE37FFAEFF253E78FD65D435" blockId="1.[151,1436,1198,1369]" pageId="1" pageNumber="554">
<emphasis id="B93EEAF6AE37FFAEFF253E78FED1D459" bold="true" box="[199,315,1307,1333]" pageId="1" pageNumber="554">Remarks.</emphasis>
This species is easily separated from other known species of the genus occurring in south eastern Asia by the antennal stylus thick, finger-like.
</paragraph>
